{DescAliveFull}{}{This is a butcher from the butchery. His clothes are covered with the brahmin's blood.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{You can feel his smell even from that distance.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{To imagine him screaming "Ahhh...fresh meat!" doesn't require much of an imagination.}
