{Speech 3}{}{@sex@|Move it, mister;|Hey lady, do you mind moving?| I've got brahmin to kill.@@Get out of the way.@@Can you please move? I've got work to do.}
{Speech 5}{}{Ahhh, time to go home and relax in my own stink.@@It's time to head home and have a nice jerky steak.@@That was a long day. I hope to god someone kills me in my sleep so I don't have to do this\n again.@@More scraps for Rose.@@Uh! I never get used to this.@@I love my work.@@Balthas will pay a pretty coin for this hide.@@I hear you can make a great dessert from the eyeball squeezin's.@@I'm about ready for a smoke.@@Jerky is good for the bones.@@Jerky is good for the hair.@@Jerky is good for the lungs.@@Jerky is good for the stomach.Jerky is good for the loins.@@Jerky tastes good.@@Christ, did a brahmin shit in here?@@I think I stained my coat. HA! HA! HA!@@Watch your step. This place is full of nasty things on the ground.@@You like jerky?@@I even like jerky for breakfast.@@Milk, ice-cream, all makes my stomach nuts. But JERKY!!!@@Hey! Listen here, JERKY!!! HA! HA! HA!}
